articles.author: Jay Croft
articles.title: Wyoming outlaws abortion pills - CNN
articles.description: As the fight over abortion pills heats up nationally, Wyoming on Friday prohibited the medication in what NARAL Pro-Choice America called a "first of its kind" law, and also enacted a near-total ban on abortion.
